{"tid":868660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李準基：我真的沒想過會出演認哥！IU：是我帶他來的！","createTime":"2018-10-19T16:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T17:57:51.000Z","uid":34643,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd275aa1e4194a85eae324cf282ff87c1284573b","tid":868660,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_fba3273a465998c1e5dcb34105d4db94/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-18/110375-666771.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_fba3273a465998c1e5dcb34105d4db94%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-18%2F110375-666771.jpg&h=f0ac1b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日，JTBC公開了李準基、IU《認識的哥哥》錄製前事先採訪的影片。<br />\n<br />\n一開始問了他們：「轉學來認哥學校的感受？」李準基表示：「很開心能夠見到只在電視中見過的前輩們，時隔很久又見到了知恩，非常非常幸福，希望今天能度過愉快的時間。」IU也說：「我也因為很久沒有出演綜藝很緊張，能夠和非常有趣的準基歐爸一起，非常踏實，會好好玩的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5f547f22534776b77ee9101ae586b6fe/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-18/110375-666770.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5f547f22534776b77ee9101ae586b6fe%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-18%2F110375-666770.png&h=9cd94e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們提到了最想見的哥哥，李準基是姜鎬童；IU是徐章勳。後來製作組請他們「互相稱讚穿校服的對方」IU説：「我對準基歐爸說了，時隔很久穿上校服粉絲們應該會很喜歡吧！真的非常適合。」李準基也說：「最近在《我的大叔》時展現深刻的演技，現在直接叫做高中生都行，太美麗了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3609668152fc3bb73f3304a12269114d/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-18/110375-666767.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3609668152fc3bb73f3304a12269114d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-18%2F110375-666767.png&h=f1fc4c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ae469841f233ecf3c16427795426fc05/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-18/110375-666766.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ae469841f233ecf3c16427795426fc05%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-18%2F110375-666766.png&h=484b34fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU介紹了這次發行的歌曲《BBIBBI》，李準基分享了近況，並提到會在12月舉行亞洲巡迴。最後李準基對觀眾們說：「《認哥》的觀眾們，我真的做夢也沒想過會透過《認哥》出演綜藝，接到了知恩的邀請來了，請大家愉快地收看。」IU在一旁說著：「是我帶他來的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_417fd3a705b68f042e593ef4e9f8d071/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-18/110375-666768.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_417fd3a705b68f042e593ef4e9f8d071%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-18%2F110375-666768.png&h=87241459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b113beed99027220eeca0367aa307b8e/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-18/110375-666769.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b113beed99027220eeca0367aa307b8e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-18%2F110375-666769.png&h=b5788f12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看完真的覺得兩人感情很好，讓人更加期待本週的播出啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9vCM-kuM22U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9vCM-kuM22U&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=86759a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9vCM-kuM22U</a>"},{"pid":"a9facea762618bdb2e26ad56d01627bb970ff7d0","tid":868660,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"李準基搞乜撚"},{"pid":"142be90ae900707fefb0e624075f8371dcdac38e","tid":868660,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9facea762618bdb2e26ad56d01627bb970ff7d0","tid":868660,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"李準基搞乜撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"做咩? 唔同左樣???"},{"pid":"206017dd44a6b97f243543ff4af4b40c0bc5f793","tid":868660,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:15: